You are an experienced burglar, smuggler, fence, pickpocket, or some other criminal. You have survived up to this point by flouting the rules and regulations of society.

Gain the language [[thieves' cant]]. In addition, gain an [[advantage]] when using [[thieves' tools]]. You also have one reliable and trustworthy contact who acts as your liaison to a network of other criminals.

See also [[Underhanded]] and [[I Know A Guy]].